snippet.title: Celebrity Loop
snippet.description:
The best source for celebrity drama on YouTube! You can find anything from the newest celebrity gossip to celebrity news updates on trending events in our videos! Thank you for watching!

I spend a lot of time creating each and every one of my videos! Let me show you my process: First I do the research, staying up-to-date in the celebrity world requires spending a lot of time on social media and different media outlets! Then I write a script for it and additionally record the audio for the video. 

Once that is all perfect, I edit the video and make sure I include relevant footage that makes the video interesting to watch. This is the most time-consuming part and can take anywhere from 2-5 hours per video! Once that's done I upload the video and hope that you guys enjoy it!

Looking forward to seeing you in my future videos! Thanks!
